verbiste.el is a package allowing to use the [http://www3.sympatico.ca/sarrazip/dev/verbiste.html verbiste] program to conjugate/deconjugate French verbs.

It is available as a Git repository :

<code>
git clone git://gaffer.ptitcanardnoir.org/verbiste-el.git
</code>

I have made a different version which has (I think) a nicer display:

http://kanis.fr/hg/lisp/ivan/verbiste.el

http://kanis.fr/verbiste.jpg

